    "Please see Fig. 12.",
    "First, we asked whether their respective institutions have provided trainings for the effective and ethical use of the tools in question.",
    "A significant majority of 78 percent said they have not undergone training, while the rest (22%) have received such training.",
    "Again, this finding corroborates our previous finding in Part 1 (Perceptions) and Part 2 (Practices).",
    "Second, we asked if their institutions have provided guidelines for using the tools in question."
